<h3>How to add a new user setting</h3>
<ol>
    <li>Add setting property to Settings entity (symfony console make:entity | Settings)</li>
    <li>Update the Database (symfony console doctrine:schema:update --force)</li>
    <li>Update SettingType form with new property</li>
    <li>Update defaults in reg controller, register action</li>
</ol>

